## Open Core Note

This repository contains the **core** Maltheron code, which is licensed under the
MIT License above. This includes:

- Database schema (Convex)
- API logic (Elysia)
- Frontend dashboard (React)
- Protocol implementations

The **hosted Maltheron platform** is proprietary and not included in this
repository. If you're looking to run your own instance, you're free to use
the MIT-licensed code, but the Maltheron brand and trademarks remain
proprietary.

For the hosted service, visit: https://maltheron.network
